{"tid":2496354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟蘇聯解體係咩嘅原因所以解體？","createTime":"2021-04-19T18:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:25:55.000Z","uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"957e0649548a614c00eaf58b8291951a54d3e57f","tid":2496354,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:43:53.000Z","msg":"真係咁簡單因為星戰計劃令到蘇聯從經濟上崩潰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係有其他都頗為重要嘅原因？例如戈巴卓夫上台去斯太林化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係戈巴卓夫改革令到蘇聯資產階級自由化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係好似托洛斯基所說，蘇聯由一開始建立就已經注定失敗，因為佢唔係由資本主義蛻變成共產主義，而係由一個貧窮嘅封建制度蛻變成共產主義，違反馬克思嘅學說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200ce443927db2c8e5047e0f6f67d2a71c08681d","tid":2496354,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8QYz-Oq7pkI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8QYz-Oq7pkI&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=7c6d88fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8QYz-Oq7pkI</a>"},{"pid":"b41a7f1e161019a56b205a388a68cf4056e5c5d3","tid":2496354,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T18:49:47.000Z","msg":"戈爾巴喬夫為咗進行政治改革容許蘇聯任何成員國包括烏克蘭俄羅斯等等產生民主選